1
00:34:33,520 --> 00:34:37,199
👸 Hwa-jin: I think it was around
New Year last year,

2
00:34:37,200 --> 00:34:41,999
👸 Hwa-jin: A coworker and I said,
Let us try something new,

3
00:34:42,000 --> 00:34:44,899
👸 Hwa-jin: so we planned a hike.

4
00:34:44,900 --> 00:34:48,959
👸 Hwa-jin: To Achasan, probably
the easiest mountain in Seoul.

5
00:34:48,960 --> 00:34:49,959
👸 Hwa-jin: Wait, why are you laughing?

6
00:34:49,960 --> 00:34:51,838
🚶🏼‍♀️ Jin-young: It just made me think of
a subway stop.

7
00:34:51,839 --> 00:34:53,399
👸 Hwa-jin: Exactly.

8
00:34:53,400 --> 00:34:58,299
👸 Hwa-jin: It is actually a pretty
manageable mountain

9
00:34:58,300 --> 00:35:01,319
👸 Hwa-jin: for someone like me.

10
00:35:01,320 --> 00:35:03,199
👸 Hwa-jin: Achasan. That Achasan.

11
00:35:03,200 --> 00:35:05,039
👸 Hwa-jin: And there is tteokbokki
at the bottom.

12
00:35:05,040 --> 00:35:06,879
👸 Hwa-jin: That was the best
I could do.

13
00:35:06,880 --> 00:35:08,879
🤦🏻‍♀️ A-sol: So how was it,
once you got up there?

14
00:35:08,880 --> 00:35:11,719
👸 Hwa-jin: I thought,
Oh, this is doable,

15
00:35:11,720 --> 00:35:13,799
👸 Hwa-jin: which, of course,
makes sense.

16
00:35:13,800 --> 00:35:16,118
👸 Hwa-jin: I picked an easy mountain
on purpose.

17
00:35:16,119 --> 00:35:17,799
🚶🏼‍♀️ Jin-young: I do not think I have ever been

18
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:19,159
🚶🏼‍♀️ Jin-young: to any mountain
other than Namsan.

19
00:35:19,160 --> 00:35:22,759
🤦🏻‍♀️ A-sol: Then please remain silent.

20
00:35:22,760 --> 00:35:24,599
🤦🏻‍♀️ A-sol: You do not qualify.

21
00:35:24,600 --> 00:35:27,199
🤦🏻‍♀️ A-sol: You laughed the second
you heard "Achasan,"

22
00:35:27,200 --> 00:35:30,000
🤦🏻‍♀️ A-sol: and I thought you were naming
some epic mountain.
